    "description": "A comprehensive evaluation of connectivity methods for L1000 data.\n\nRCSM(Recommended Connectivity-map Scoring Methods).\n\nConnecting disease gene expression signatures to compound-induced gene expression profiles is valuable for understanding drug Mechanism of Action (MoA) and applying an existing therapeutic to a new disease indication. RCSM is an R package for measuring those connectivities. RCSM implemented seven methods that are reported in published papers.\n\n||| CORRECT NAME OF TOOL COULD ALSO BE 'Repurposing', 'ZhangScore'",
